  "2355020": {
    "name": "失落的赫尔登",
    "steam_appid": 2355020,
    "required_age": 0,
    "is_free": false,
    "description": "<p class=\"bb_paragraph\" style=\"text-align: center\"><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2355020/extras/a1fb10c574f8ce18e38f76f6068b6834.poster.avif?t=1764259846\" width=600 height=338 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2355020/extras/a1fb10c574f8ce18e38f76f6068b6834.webm?t=1764259846\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2355020/extras/a1fb10c574f8ce18e38f76f6068b6834.mp4?t=1764259846\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >在合一教的统治下，厄拉大陆的子民皆被七宗罪之一所束缚。能抵抗欲望的人将在神圣之地赫尔登获得永生，而屈服于欲望的人则将面临比死亡更可怕的命运。</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >《失落的赫尔登》是一款经典风格的日式动作角色扮演游戏，背景设定在一个精美的手绘 3D 世界中。游戏插画由绪贺岳志 (代表作《重力眩晕》) 操刀，配乐则由崎元仁 (代表作《最终幻想 XII》《最终幻想战略版》《战场女武神》) 制作。玩家将跟随 8 名可高度自定义的角色，踏上跨越厄拉大陆的旅程，掌握巧妙平衡实时与回合制战斗的阶段式战斗系统。</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" style=\"text-align: center\"><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2355020/extras/68715853eab6c5073ed09e8117857e6d.poster.avif?t=1764259846\" width=600 height=338 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2355020/extras/68715853eab6c5073ed09e8117857e6d.webm?t=1764259846\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2355020/extras/68715853eab6c5073ed09e8117857e6d.mp4?t=1764259846\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span></p><h2 class=\"bb_tag\" >原罪与自我救赎</h2><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >双胞胎的诞生被视作不祥之兆。罪缚仪式的失败导致西菲尔生而无罪，而莱赫特却被七宗罪同时缠身。这两个婴儿随后被藏匿于合一教神殿，作为信仰守护者阿克洪被抚养长大。</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >多年后，莱赫特为挣脱宿命而选择出逃。西菲尔不得不离开神殿的庇护，踏上寻找兄弟的旅途，却意外卷入了一个充斥着怪物、反叛者与天界阴谋的纷争世界。《失落的赫尔登》讲述了一段关于自我救赎、血脉亲情与宿命纠缠的精彩故事，并提供了完整的日英双语配音。</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" style=\"text-align: center\"><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2355020/extras/830dcb4b897120b4742e5e9260086ef6.poster.avif?t=1764259846\" width=600 height=338 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2355020/extras/830dcb4b897120b4742e5e9260086ef6.webm?t=1764259846\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2355020/extras/830dcb4b897120b4742e5e9260086ef6.mp4?t=1764259846\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span></p><h2 class=\"bb_tag\" >全新战斗形式</h2><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >独特的阶段式战斗系统融合了实时战斗的热血刺激与回合制战斗的战术深度。在对抗怪物与神祇的战斗中，玩家需巧妙把握攻击时机、角色站位、元素属性配合及全员指令运用。通过发动强大的超越技能来扭转战局，并可借助多层职业体系、技能树和丰富的装备选择，调整队伍配置，取得战斗胜利。</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" style=\"text-align: center\"><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2355020/extras/dca61b069ab34ea1216b255a9c285914.poster.avif?t=1764259846\" width=600 height=338 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2355020/extras/dca61b069ab34ea1216b255a9c285914.webm?t=1764259846\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2355020/extras/dca61b069ab34ea1216b255a9c285914.mp4?t=1764259846\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span></p><h2 class=\"bb_tag\" >探索广袤世界</h2><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >得益于绪贺岳志 (代表作《重力眩晕》) 参与设计的独特手绘“深层 2D”美术风格，玩家将仿佛置身于经典 JRPG 的画卷世界。《失落的赫尔登》的艺术表现力更由崎元仁 (代表作《最终幻想 XII》《最终幻想战略版》《战场女武神》) 创作的恢弘配乐注入了灵魂。</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" style=\"text-align: center\"><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2355020/extras/b5af4d000732f3671ae62633decb1b4c.poster.avif?t=1764259846\" width=600 height=338 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2355020/extras/b5af4d000732f3671ae62633decb1b4c.webm?t=1764259846\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2355020/extras/b5af4d000732f3671ae62633decb1b4c.mp4?t=1764259846\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >这个世界的每个角落都暗藏玄机：探索未知领域，寻找隐藏物品、收藏品及敌人；善用天气变化与特殊技能，解锁 NPC，开拓新区域；帮助旅途中遇到的人，或在厄拉大陆最风靡的桌游“六角棋”中消磨时光。</p>",
